        <p style="text-align:left; font-size:1.1em; margin-bottom:2rem;">
          Welcome to the official guide to our proprietary analytics. This glossary explains the key metrics we use to evaluate player and character performance in the competitive scene. You’ll find quick definitions, links to examples, and related pages like the <a href="/fgpi/">Fighting Game Performance Index (FGPI)</a>, <a href="/player-stats/">Player Stats</a>, and <a href="/character-stats/">Character Stats &amp; CPV</a>.
